languages.text: "Слушаюсь, Лорд-капитан. Вахта на корабле прошла без инцидентов... Без инцидентов, угрожающих безопасности корабля и экипажа. Ситуация штатная".
"Yes, {mf|sir|ma'am}, Lord Captain! The last watch passed without incident... At least, none that jeopardised the safety of the vessel and her crew. The situation is under control."

languages.text: “遵命，舰长大人。上次轮班没有发生任何事故……至少没有威胁到舰船与船员的安全。局势已经得到了控制。”
languages.original_text: "Yes, {mf|sir|ma'am}, Lord Captain! The last watch passed without incident... At least, none that jeopardised the safety of the vessel and her crew. The situation is under control."

traits.locale_text: “啊，啊，遵命，舰长大人。上次轮班没有发生任何事故……至少没有威胁到舰船与船员的安全。局势已经得到了控制。”

languages.text: "Jawohl, {mf|Sir|Ma'am}, Lord Captain. In der letzten Wache gab es keine Zwischenfälle ... Jedenfalls keine, die die Sicherheit des Schiffs und seiner Crew gefährdet hätten. Die Situation ist unter Kontrolle."
languages.original_text: "Yes, {mf|sir|ma'am}, Lord Captain! The last watch passed without incident... At least, none that jeopardised the safety of the vessel and her crew. The situation is under control."

traits.locale_text: "Aye, aye, Lord Captain. Es gab während der letzten Wache keinerlei Vorfälle ... Zumindest keine, welche die Sicherheits des Schiffs und seiner Crew gefährdet hätten. Die Situation ist unter Kontrolle."

languages.text: «¡Entendido, Lord Capitán! No ha habido incidentes en la última guardia... Al menos ninguno que haya alterado la seguridad de la nave ni de su tripulación. La situación está bajo control».
languages.original_text: "Yes, {mf|sir|ma'am}, Lord Captain! The last watch passed without incident... At least, none that jeopardised the safety of the vessel and her crew. The situation is under control."

traits.locale_text: «Entendido, Lord Capitán. No ha habido incidentes en la última guardia... Al menos ninguno que haya alterado la seguridad de la nave ni de su tripulación. La situación está bajo control».

languages.text: 「御意に、ロード・キャプテン！前回の見張りでは特に何もありませんでした…少なくとも、船とクルーの安全を危険にさらすようなものはありませんでした。状況はコントロール下にあります」
languages.original_text: "Yes, {mf|sir|ma'am}, Lord Captain! The last watch passed without incident... At least, none that jeopardised the safety of the vessel and her crew. The situation is under control."

languages.text: "Emredersiniz Lord Kaptan! Son nöbette herhangi bir olay yaşanmadı. Daha doğrusu geminin ve mürettebatının güvenliğini tehlikeye atan bir şey olmadı. Durum kontrol altında."
languages.original_text: "Yes, {mf|sir|ma'am}, Lord Captain! The last watch passed without incident... At least, none that jeopardised the safety of the vessel and her crew. The situation is under control."

traits.locale_text: "Evet efendim, Lord Kaptan! Son nöbette herhangi bir olay yaşanmadı. En azından geminin ve mürettebatının güvenliğini tehlikeye atan bir olay. Durum kontrol altında."
